title: IMAX.Africa.The.Serengeti.720p.HDTV.DivX6.AC3
description: AFRICA: THE SERENGETI brings to life the incredible story of the greatest migration of land animals anywhere on earth. The first African epic filmed in large format, the film takes viewers on a journey with more than 1.5 million animals as they travel over 500 miles across the plains of the Serengeti, a place where life and death dramas are played daily within the most important animal sanctuary on earth.
